Take your Chrome extension experience to the next level with Extension Stats Analyzer! This powerful Chrome extension acts as your comprehensive metrics dashboard, providing valuable insights into the world of Chrome extensions.

Empowering Extension Ecosystem:

Extension Stats Analyzer is committed to making Chrome extension metrics more accessible to everyone. It opens doors for competitive analysis, supports ethical extension development, and helps users make informed choices.

For Developers: We offer extension developers a chance to shine in the crowded marketplace. Our friendly tools assist in analyzing extension performance in the Chrome Web Store, allowing developers to refine their products and compete effectively.

For Users and Organizations: Regain control over your browsing experience with insights into the risk factors associated with each extension. Quickly identify high-risk extensions and make informed decisions to enhance your digital security.

Whether you're a developer aiming for success in the Chrome Web Store or a user looking to optimize your browsing experience, Extension Stats Analyzer is your trusted companion. Make informed decisions, support quality extensions, and ensure your Chrome browser is performing at its best.

Download Extension Stats Analyzer today and embark on a journey to understand, enhance, and secure your Chrome extension ecosystem!
